## [V-009] AddDelegate `D.l` â€” `pending_data` `Intent.parseUri(str, 1)` Sink With **NO** Package Check

**File:** `sources/com/samsung/android/app/reminder/ui/detail/add/D.java` (lines 735â€“762)
**Severity:** Critical â€” reachable via V-001 chain, no guard at all on the reconstructed Intent.
**Class of flaw:** CWE-436 / CWE-470 / CWE-116 â€” attacker-controlled string deserialised into a fully-functional Intent with no allow-list.

