After `D.l(Intent)` finishes its normal wiring, it checks for a `pending_request` extra and replays a *saved* activity result:

```java
Intent intent6 = this.f29992d;  // attacker-controlled intent
if (intent6 != null && intent6.hasExtra("pending_request")) {
    final int intExtra3 = this.f29992d.getIntExtra("pending_request", -1);
    final int intExtra4 = this.f29992d.getIntExtra("pending_result", -2);
    Optional optionalOfNullable8 = Optional.ofNullable(this.f29992d);
