## [V-018] `m9.c` LocationShareIntentParser â€” Confirmed Arbitrary-Geofence Injection + HOME/WORK Coordinate Exfiltration

**File:** `sources/m9/c.java` (143 lines)
**Severity:** Critical â€” chain with V-015 + V-016 gives a **one-click web attack** that:
* creates a geofence reminder with attacker-chosen coordinates/radius, **or**
